Not quite a clone of the original as the author states but it sure is a delicious vape, tasty as hell, smooth,sweet, delicious and chain vapeable. &#xD;
I also made a tweaked version with 5% cap blueberry and 2% Bluberry xtra for a slightly more blue taste and mixxed with only 1% sweetener. &#xD;
&#xD;
Well done Bevlar for a solid and super tasty recipe.
